Retrieve classification above the taxon

Source: R/rt_taxa_parent.R
rt_taxa_parent.Rd

Retrieve classification above the taxon

rt_taxa_parent(id)

Arguments

id

integer(1)
an integer giving the id of the taxon in TaxRef (also called cdNom)

Examples

rt_taxa_parent(id = 443800)
